Description: Extended version of 'factoextra' with modernized code for compatibility
    with current R ecosystem (ggplot2 3.5.2+, R 4.1.0+). Provides easy-to-use
    functions to extract and visualize the output of multivariate data analyses,
    including 'PCA' (Principal Component Analysis), 'CA' (Correspondence Analysis),
    'MCA' (Multiple Correspondence Analysis), 'FAMD' (Factor Analysis of Mixed Data),
    'MFA' (Multiple Factor Analysis) and 'HMFA' (Hierarchical Multiple Factor Analysis)
    functions from different R packages. It contains also functions for simplifying
    some clustering analysis steps and provides 'ggplot2'-based elegant data visualization.
